# Demo videos — all compressed to *-web.mp4 (0.9–5MB each) and self-hosted.
# Raw originals stay excluded: bite-balance.mp4 (174MB) and
# algo-visualizer.mp4 (109MB) exceed GitHub's 100MB limit.
# All *-web.mp4 versions are allow-listed.
assets/videos/*.mp4
!assets/videos/*-web.mp4

# Local drop zone for candidate certificate images not ready to publish yet.
# To go live: copy the file into assets/certificates/ and name it the next
# number (1.jpg, 2.jpg, ...) — js/certificates.js auto-discovers it, no code
# edits needed. This folder itself isn't part of the deployed site.
Course_Certificates/
